These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, august, october, september
1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | september | july | october | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, chess, bridge, billiard
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
4. the person playing chess is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
8. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | chess  | bridge    | scrabble | billiard    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, rock-climbing, puzzles, card-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, electrician, police-officer
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the coach##6
2. the doctor is not the person who's hobby is puzzles##6
3. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
4. the doctor is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
7. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
8. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | card-games       | rock-climbing  | board-games  | puzzles |
| Job        | electrician | police-officer | doctor | coach  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog, snake
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, designer, chef, architect
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
3. the architect is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6
4. the architect is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
5. the chef is on the right of the designer##1
6. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the architect##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | hedgehog | snake     | goldfish |
| Transport   | designer     | chef    | manager | architect    |

