.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, reading, board-games, chess
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
5. the person watching spy movies is the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
7. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
8. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5
9. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy    | disaster  | thriller   |
| Nationality   | board-games  | chess | reading | skydiving |

