.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, spy, time-travel, zombie
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, tea, milk
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking tea is not the person watching spy movies##6
3. the person watching documentary movies is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
6. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | spy     | time-travel | documentary |
| Music-Genre   | tea | iced-tea | milk      | coffee         |

