5. the mexican is on the left or right of the journalist##3
6. the coach is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
7. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
8. the colombian is not the social-worker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
