2. the person driving the helicopter is not the fan techno##6
3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the fan soul##5
4. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the subway is the fan soul##1
7. the fan blues is not the person driving the subway##6
8. the fan folk is somewhere to the right of the fan techno##5

.:: Answer ::.
