.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, august, november
1. the person who's birthday is in july is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
6. the person who's birthday is in june is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | ferret        | rabbit  | fish     |
| Sport   | july     | november | june | august |

