The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, snowmobile, trike
1. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
2. the person playing whist is not the person driving the bike##6
3. the person driving the bus is the person playing whist##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not the person playing whist##6
6. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person driving the bike##6
7. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
8. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | monopoly  | snooker | mah-jongg | whist |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike     | trike     | bus    |

