2. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
4. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
7. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2      |       3       |       4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving  | photography | chess         | rock-climbing |
| Sport   | london | venice  | hamburg | nizza       |

