1. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
6. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea | water      | mirinda   |
| Transport   | goat  | rat   | turtle | rabbit |

 